#: citizens.html.j2:27
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Taler uses modern cryptography, ensuring that there\n"
#| "is no counterfeit.  Your digital wallet is safer\n"
#| "than your physical wallet.  At most, you can lose\n"
